item.dc:creator: @I_Forca_I I Forca I
item.description:
@I_Forca_I wrote:

[quote=“the cow slay, post:4, topic:103372”][center]Before reading on, you should probably know that my online computer is a bit dodgey at the moment, so i do all my coding on my OFFLINE computer! I am quite often online and i can very easily transfer files from one computer to the next, so i should still be able to send you stuff

What will be your name on the forums: The Cow Slay
What are you applying for: Forum Mod AND Coder
Experiences: I have moderated many many forums in my time, alot of them to do with javascript, or HTML related stuff (even some runescape fan sites back when i used to play! LOL!!!) Also i have been coding now for quite a long time and think i will be able to come up with some good ideas, and unlike some coders im not messy! I like to keep things organised in voids and i know what im doing!
Why should i choose you: I enjoy helping people, i have moderated lots before so i know what to move/lock/delete and whom to warn etc. I always keep track of the rules making sure i dont break any of them myself (always try to set a good example!!!) And you should choose me because what i said in Experiences ^^ Even though i am busy with my own server, i would gladly put it asside to help you!
How Can i contact you: Well im not on msn anymore, but i dont know you well egnough to give you my number. So i guess if you want to contact me you should just gimme a mail at my temp address untill i get my new addresses up: Bishop.WebDesign@googlemail.com[/center][/quote]

Accepted for Forum mod and coder
